'''Navshe'starn''' was a [[City/Legends|city]] on the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. 

It was located in the eastern part of the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] western continent, halfway between the cities [[Covepi'starn]] (to the northwest) and [[Gna She'starn]] (to the southeast).

